      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is Databox?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://join.databox.com/vpct6npxonaf"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Databox is a business analytics platform that connects all your tools—like HubSpot, Google Analytics 4, and Facebook Ads—into one real-time dashboard. It's built to help teams visualize KPIs instantly, without the hassle of manual data pulls. I love how it turns scattered metrics into clear, actionable insights. Ready to experience it? ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start your free Databox trial",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and see why thousands of companies rely on it daily.",
            "marks": []
