            "_type": "span",
            "text": "databox.com",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and create a free account. The free tier includes 3 data sources and 50 AI credits monthly—perfect for small teams or solo entrepreneurs. No credit card is needed, so you can experiment risk-free.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Connect Your Data Sources",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Once logged in, go to \"Data Sources\" and link your tools. Databox supports 100+ integrations, from Google Sheets to Stripe. I connected my HubSpot and Google Analytics 4 accounts in a few clicks. The syncing is real-time, so your data stays fresh.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 3: Build Your First Dashboard",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use the drag-and-drop builder to create a dashboard. Start with a template—like the \"Marketing Overview\"—or build from scratch. Add metrics like revenue, website traffic, or ad spend. I customized one to track my blog performance alongside social media stats, all in one view.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 4: Leverage AI with Genie",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/databox-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Activate the AI Genie feature to ask questions like, \"What was our sales growth last month?\" It analyzes your data and provides instant summaries. This feature saves me hours of manual analysis each week. Learn more about how to maximize it in our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "tips and best practices",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
